The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                               IN THE CITY
                  
	 CESC SC beat SC Railway 2-0 in a league match of the 113th All-India Beighton Cup at the SAI Eastern Complex on Thursday. In another match, Tamil Nadu XI defeated BNR Recreation Club 3-2.          
	 Mohammed Sarfaraz and Aandrita Deb advanced to the finals of both the singles and doubles of boys and girls under-16 event respectively of the Senco Calcutta Gymkhana Grass Court Tennis Tournament 2008 played at the Gymkhana on Thursday. Meanwhile, in the mens final, Vinod Sewa will face Farid Alam. In the womens semi-final Treta Bhattacharya beat Arundhuti Basu 6-1, 6-1. She will now face Raseena Chablani in the final.                
	CHESS: State meet at Kshudiram Anushilan Kendra from 2pm      
	HOCKEY: Beighton Cup at SAI Complex from 12.30pm      
	TENNIS: Calcutta Gymkhana Grass Court meet at the club                                                                                                                                                                       
